    "gateCode": "USER-ALL OR ADMIN-ACCESS",
    "behaviour": "UPDATE USER + implicit CHANGE-PASSWORD + the de-facto ACTIVATE/DEACTIVATE path. UserResource.java:158. No dedicated change-password or activate endpoint exists; password is changed via the User body (blank=keep, non-blank=re-encode, UserServiceImpl.java:121-125). Self activate/deactivate blocked at controller (lines 166-170); root may only be activated/deactivated. CAVEAT: service hardcodes user.setActive(true) on every update (UserServiceImpl.java:126, comment 'before implementing activate and deactivate user') so deactivate is effectively a no-op stub."
